      "content": "Wait, we're behind? If I report a delay or a \"Red\" status to the board tomorrow, they're going to freeze the budget for the entire Q4 cycle. We cannot afford a status change right now. Is there really no way to categorize this as \"At Risk\" or \"Green with caveats\" instead of an outright delay? Can't we just say we're navigating some minor bottlenecks?",
